{"title":"Tree","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":64,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/tyvj-2361","statement":[{"title":"","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"\n# \n\n \n # 题目描述 \n<p>\n给你一棵TREE,以及这棵树上边的距离.问有多少对点它们两者间的距离小于等于K\r<br></p> \n\n \n # 输入格式 \n<p>\nN（n<=40000）\r<br>接下来n-1行边描述管道，按照题目中写的输入\r<br>接下来是k\r<br></p> \n\n \n # 输出格式 \n<p>\n一行，有多少对点之间的距离小于等于k\r<br></p> "},{"title":"样例数据","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"<style>\n        table,table tr th, table tr td { border:1px solid #0094ff; }\n        table { width: 200px; min-height: 25px; line-height: 25px; text-align: center; border-collapse: collapse;}   \n    </style>\n<table>\n\t<tr>\n\t\t<td>输入样例</td>\n\t\t<td>输出样例</td>\n\t</tr>\n<tr><td>7\r\n1 6 13 \r\n6 3 9 \r\n3 5 7 \r\n4 1 3 \r\n2 4 20 \r\n4 7 2 \r\n10\r\n</td><td>5</td></tr></table>\n\n"}]}